Skinny Tuna Salad Recipe 🥗
Ingredients:
- 2 eggs
- lettuce
- half a cucumber 
- green onion
- 1 can of canned tuna (in water)
- half a can of corn
- Greek yoghurt (~2 tablespoons)
- Dijon Mustard ( ~1 tablespoon)
- Salt & Pepper to taste
- * sometimes I add chickpeas for extra fiber!

Hard boil 2 eggs, let them chill in cold water for 5 mins for easy peeling. Finely chop all of the ingredients & add them to the salad bowl. Drain the tuna, add it to the bowl as well. Add the Greek yoghurt & mustard. Mix everything well and here you have it - my favorite salad with tons of protein 🤍 enjoyyyy
